# Music

Background music tracks for different scenes.

## Recommended Files

- menu_theme.ogg - Main menu background music
- stage1_theme.ogg - Stage 1 music
- stage2_theme.ogg - Stage 2 music
- boss_theme.ogg - Boss battle music
- victory_jingle.ogg - Stage clear/victory music
- gameover.ogg - Game over music

Use .ogg format for best compression. Ensure tracks loop seamlessly!

Ask @audio to implement music playback and crossfading!
